## Skills Router 完整路由表

### 6种意图 × 渠道选择

```javascript
decision_maker_search: {   // ⭐ LinkedIn决策人搜索（已修正2026-04-01）
  domestic:  [
    { skill: 'exa-free-via-mcporter', priority: 5, desc: 'Exa Free via mcporter，无需API Key' },
    { skill: 'exa-search', priority: 3, desc: 'Exa API版本（需要EXA_API_KEY）' }
  ],
  overseas:  [
    { skill: 'exa-free-via-mcporter', priority: 5, desc: 'Exa Free via mcporter，无需API Key' },
    { skill: 'exa-search', priority: 3, desc: 'Exa API版本（需要EXA_API_KEY）' }
  ],
  fallback: [
    { skill: 'web_search', priority: 1, desc: 'Google搜索（LinkedIn有限制）' }
  ]
}

customer_discovery: {        // 客户发现
  domestic:  ['weibo', 'wechat', 'baidu'],
  overseas:  ['teyi', 'exa-search', 'facebook']
}

company_research: {           // 企业背调
  domestic:  ['baidu'],
  overseas:  ['teyi', 'exa-search']
}

email_outreach: {             // 邮件触达
  domestic:  ['email-sender', 'delivery-queue'],
  overseas:  ['delivery-queue', 'email-sender', 'email-outreach-ops']
}

social_media_outreach: {      // 社媒运营 ⭐新增
  facebook:   ['ai-social-media-content', 'facebook-acquisition'],
  instagram:  ['ai-social-media-content'],
  linkedin:   ['ai-social-media-content', 'linkedin-writer']
}

full_pipeline: {
  overseas:  ['acquisition-coordinator']
}
```

### 故障自动切换（已修正2026-04-01）

| 主渠道 | 不可用时切换 | 说明 |
|--------|-------------|------|
| LinkedIn MCP via mcporter | → Exa Free via mcporter | LinkedIn服务需要启动，Exa Free现成可用 |
| Exa Free via mcporter | → Exa API (exa-search) | 如果mcporter不可用，用exa-search（需API Key）|
| Exa API (exa-search) | → web_search (Google) | 最后降级，LinkedIn可能受限 |
| teyi | → exa-search + customs | 特易RPA失败时用Exa+海关数据 |
| email-sender | → delivery-queue | 邮件发送队列降级 |

